    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/1c342cffb02bd9639983d93d05e2e6d3.avif?t=1732711329\" width=462 height=174 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >背景简介</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >桃李村是一座大山里的村子，离镇子有20分钟车程，其周边有一些种植基地，有部分员工会图方便到村里租房暂住。村子里很和睦，大家彼此都认识。这年10月，在外上大学的主角接到刘婶的电话，得知母亲生重病而回乡探望，故事就由此开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/62e66753e39016bb3b972163fa489d38.avif?t=1732711329\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras_big/62e66753e39016bb3b972163fa489d38.avif?t=1732711329 width=800 height=400 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以第一人称视角探索这熟悉而又陌生的村庄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >得知这场布局背后的由来和原因。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/d0b073559ed6905a513fa606e3feb754.poster.avif?t=1732711329\" width=800 height=428 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/d0b073559ed6905a513fa606e3feb754.webm?t=1732711329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/d0b073559ed6905a513fa606e3feb754.mp4?t=1732711329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事分明线和暗线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >明线为主线剧情，揭示了异常的原因。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >暗线穿插于主线里，需要探索村庄，找到最初的起因。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部分开放式地图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/f23cf643080687759c3d836eb39fc017.avif?t=1732711329\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras_big/f23cf643080687759c3d836eb39fc017.avif?t=1732711329 width=800 height=396 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此游戏致曾经同舍友一起玩恐怖游戏的欢乐时光，愿珍惜。</p>",
